            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, add your <strong>cashew nuts</strong> and <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until slightly darkened in colour</p><p>Tip: Watch these like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once toasted, remove the tray from the oven and set aside to cool – these are your <strong>toasted nuts & seeds</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1690285690927-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1690285690927-x400.jpg",
